Package: sims
Title: Simulate Datasets from 'JAGS' or R Code
Version: 0.0.0.9024
Authors@R: c(
    person("Audrey", "Beliveau", , "audrey.beliveau@uwaterloo.ca", "aut"),
    person("Joe", "Thorley", , "joe@poissonconsulting.ca", c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7683-4592"))
    )
Description: Generates datasets from 'JAGS' or R code for use in simulation studies.
    The datasets are returned as an 'nlists' object and/or saved to file as 
    individual '.rds' files.
License: GPL-3
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.3),
    purrr
