    yesno,
    chk,
    nlist (>= 0.2.0),
    parallel,
    furrr,
    rjags
Suggests: 
    covr,
    future,
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
SystemRequirements: JAGS
Encoding: UTF-8
